# Repository-root ignore, applied to every Vercel project in this repo.
#
# Do NOT add package.json, pnpm-lock.yaml, pnpm-workspace.yaml or nx.json here.
# They were previously excluded, which caused two separate failures:
#   - the frontend could not run `pnpm install --frozen-lockfile` (no lockfile), so it
#     was pinned to --no-frozen-lockfile, defeating the guarantee the lockfile exists for;
#   - the cms-mcp function could not resolve its workspace dependency at runtime, and
#     every invocation failed before any handler ran.
# The workspace manifests are small and both projects need them.
#
# Leading slashes anchor to the repository root. Without them, gitignore semantics match
# a directory of that name at ANY depth — which silently excluded packages/cms-mcp/api/.
/api/
/docs/
/scripts/
/uploads/
*.log
